              },
              {
                "paragraphOrdinal": 2,
                "paragraphTitle": null,
                "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                "paragraphContents": [
                  "In wh- questions we use a question word (for example what, where, when …) before do."
                ]
              },
              {
                "paragraphOrdinal": 3,
                "paragraphTitle": null,
                "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                "paragraphContents": [
                  "To give short answers to yes/no questions we use do or don't."
